<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yā shāng de lú wěi tā bù zhé duàn 迦南553</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yā shāng de lú wěi, tā bù zhé duàn, jiāng cán de dēng huǒ tā bù chuī miè;
 měi dāng wǒ yī rén dú zì liú lèi, tā zǒng shì zhàn zài wǒ shēn biān.
 a--a--yā shāng de lú wěi tā bù zhé duàn,
 a--a--jiāng cán de dēng huǒ tā bù chuī miè;</lyrics>
<hymn_number>553</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>